		<div id="comment_body_64264536"><p>Or their definition of &ldquo;microplastics&rdquo; is faulty.</p><p>Exactly what kind of detector finds &ldquo;microplastics&rdquo;?  Do you have to burn the sample and get a chemical spectrograph?  X-ray it?  Chemically analyze it for some sort of specific molecule ?</p><p>This smells like someone is playing fast and loose with definitions, and because of that, the results don&rsquo;t make sense.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64264536">

</div>
